description:
Create src/components/tick-detail-drawer.ts using Shoelace sl-drawer:

@customElement('tick-detail-drawer')
export class TickDetailDrawer extends LitElement {
  @property() tick: Tick | null = null;
  @property({ type: Boolean }) open = false;
}

Features:
- sl-drawer slides in from right (420px width on desktop)
- Display all tick fields: ID, title, type, priority, status, description
- Show parent epic link if applicable
- Show blockers list with links
- Show blocked-by list with links
- Created/updated timestamps
- Labels display
- Close button and overlay click to close
- Emit 'drawer-close' event

Test: Open drawer with mock tick, verify all fields render, close works
